metadata.name: Spottie WiFi's ApeFest 2022 Set List
metadata.description:
Own a piece of history from ApeFest 2022, and contribute to a timely and important cause in support of women's reproductive rights.

The winner of this 1 of 1 auction will receive the framed physical set list which was hand-written by Spottie WiFi for his ApeFest 2022 performance, as well as his physical artist wristband from the event. All proceeds from the auction will be donated to LegalAbortion.eth which was established by UnicornDAO to contribute directly to leading reproductive rights nonprofits. 

On June 23, 2022, Spottie WiFi performed at Pier 17 in New York City as the opening act on the fourth and final night of ApeFest 2022. Spottie brought out legendary artists Bun B and Jim Jones during his set, which was followed by performances by Lil Wayne and Snoop Dogg, as well as an appearance and music video debut by Eminem.
